---

<section id="why-us" class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <span
        class="text-accent uppercase text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] block mb-4"
        >Neden Biz?</span
      >
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-primary leading-tight mb-6"
      >
        Mükemmellik, Detaylarda Gizlidir.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 font-light text-lg">
        Sadece bir operasyon değil, hayalinizdeki değişime giden yolda lüks ve
        güven dolu bir deneyim sunuyoruz.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <!-- Feature 1: 3D Simulation -->
      <div
        class="group p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-accent group-hover:bg-white/10 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-scan-face"
            ><path d="M3 7V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path
              d="M17 3h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2"></path><path
              d="M21 17v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><path
              d="M7 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-2"></path><rect
              width="10"
              height="8"
              x="7"
              y="8"
              rx="2"></rect><path d="M9 12h6"></path><path d="M15 12v-2"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          3D Simülasyon
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 font-light group-hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors leading-relaxed"
        >
          Ameliyat öncesi, yeni burnunuzun yüzünüzde nasıl duracağını gerçeğe en
          yakın şekilde dijital ortamda tasarlıyoruz. Yüzünüzün altın oranını
          koruyarak, size özel bir tasarım sunuyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: High Tech -->
      <div
        class="group p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-accent group-hover:bg-white/10 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-zap"
            ><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"
            ></polygon></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          Piezo Teknolojisi
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 font-light group-hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors leading-relaxed"
        >
          Ultrasonik ses dalgaları ile kemik şekillendirme yapıyoruz. Bu sayede
          yumuşak dokular zarar görmez, morluk ve şişlikler minimuma iner,
          iyileşme hızlanır.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Personal Experience -->
      <div
        class="group p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-accent group-hover:bg-white/10 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-shield-check"
            ><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path><path
              d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          Yüksek Hijyen & Güven
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 font-light group-hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors leading-relaxed"
        >
          Ameliyatlarımızı tam teşekküllü, son teknolojiye sahip A+ hastanelerde
          gerçekleştiriyoruz. Güvenliğiniz bizim için her şeyden önce gelir.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: VIP Support -->
      <div
        class="group p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-accent group-hover:bg-white/10 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-crown"
            ><path d="m2 4 3 12h14l3-12-6 7-4-7-4 7-6-7zm3 16h14"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          VIP Hizmet
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 font-light group-hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors leading-relaxed"
        >
          Şehir dışından ve yurt dışından gelen misafirlerimiz için lüks
          konaklama ve özel transfer hizmetleri organize ediyoruz. İzmir'de
          kendinizi evinizde hissedeceksiniz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5: Natural Results -->
      <div
        class="group p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-accent group-hover:bg-white/10 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-flower"
            ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path
              d="M12 16.5A4.5 4.5 0 1 1 7.5 12 4.5 4.5 0 1 1 12 7.5 4.5 4.5 0 1 1 16.5 12 4.5 4.5 0 1 1 12 16.5"
            ></path><path d="M12 7.5V2"></path><path d="M12 22v-5.5"
            ></path><path d="M16.5 12H22"></path><path d="M7.5 12H2"
            ></path><path d="m5.8 5.8 3.2 3.2"></path><path d="m15 15 3.2 3.2"
            ></path><path d="m5.8 18.2 3.2-3.2"></path><path d="m15 9 3.2-3.2"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          Doğal ve Fonksiyonel
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 font-light group-hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors leading-relaxed"
        >
          Sadece güzel görünümlü değil, aynı zamanda sağlıklı nefes alan
          burunlar hedefliyoruz. Ameliyat sonrası sürecinizde fonksiyonelliği
          asla feda etmeyiz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6: Continuous Support -->
      <div
        class="group p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-accent group-hover:bg-white/10 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-heart-handshake"
            ><path
              d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"
            ></path><path
              d="M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08v0c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66"
            ></path><path d="m18 15-2-2"></path><path d="m15 18-2-2"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          7/24 Yanınızdayız
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 font-light group-hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors leading-relaxed"
        >
          Ameliyat sonrasındaki tüm iyileşme sürecinde uzman ekibimizle bir
          telefon kadar uzağınızdayız. Sorularınıza anında cevap, kaygılarınıza
          çözüm sunuyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
